      <url>/2022/07/08/%E3%80%8A%E9%9D%92%E6%9D%8F%E5%B0%8F%C2%B7%E6%9C%AA%E5%BF%85%E5%A8%87%E5%AE%B9%E5%B0%86%E9%95%9C%E5%80%9F%E3%80%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html>    <body>        <div style="width: 450px;" mar>            <p class="ttps" align="center">《青杏小·未必娇容将镜借》</p>            <p align="center">少拾清欢，小梦酒醉，醒来换了岁月。</p>            <p align="center">好在微疏，幸也偷得昨月夜。</p>            <p align="center">痴迟灯浅，小炉可温，莫道春风不烈。</p>            <p align="center">吹皱一湖，未必娇容将镜借。</p>            <p align="right" >——落云【青杏小】</p>        </div>        <div align="center"><img src="/imgs/psc5.jpg" width="58%"></div>        <p align="center" >文中图片来自网络，如有侵权烦请联系，我会立即删除！</p>    </body>    <head>        <meta charset="utf-8">        <style type="text/css">            p{font-size: 16px;}            .ttps{font-size: 18px;}            div{margin: 0px auto;}        </style>    </head></html>]]></content>
      
      
      
