      <url>/2022/07/08/%E3%80%8A%E9%9D%92%E6%9D%8F%E5%B0%8F%C2%B7%E6%B8%B8%E6%AD%A4%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E6%95%85%E8%BE%9E%E8%BA%AB%E3%80%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html>    <body>        <div style="width: 450px;" mar>            <p class="ttps" align="center">《青杏小·游此一方故辞身》</p>            <p align="center">去了秋儿，最是安了，不知冬初还是春？</p>            <p align="center">少许闲阳，几点烟雨也是恩。</p>            <p align="center">拾光一早，碎月两半，柔柔新酒慢慢温。</p>            <p align="center">忘往远却，游此一方故辞身。</p>            <p align="right" >——落云【青杏小】</p>        </div>        <div align="center"><img src="/imgs/psc1.jpg" width="58%"></div>        <p align="center" >文中图片来自网络，如有侵权烦请联系，我会立即删除！</p>    </body>    <head>        <meta charset="utf-8">        <style type="text/css">            p{font-size: 16px;}            .ttps{font-size: 18px;}            div{margin: 0px auto;}        </style>    </head></html>]]></content>
      
      
      
