        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html>    <body>        <div style="width: 450px;" mar>            <p class="ttps" align="center">《青杏小·许是相思酒难藏》</p>            <p align="center">初楚俏小，粉璞娇玉，柔雪就了流霜。</p>            <p align="center">郁郁轻晓，怠慢了缱绻灯凉。</p>            <p align="center">唇蜜舌香，濡沫腻语，旧衣换了红裳。</p>            <p align="center">缓缓归矣，许是相思酒难藏！</p>            <p align="right" >——落云【青杏小】</p>        </div>        <div align="center"><img src="/imgs/psb3.jpg" width="58%"></div>        <p align="center" >文中图片来自网络，如有侵权烦请联系，我会立即删除！</p>    </body>    <head>        <meta charset="utf-8">        <style type="text/css">            p{font-size: 16px;}            .ttps{font-size: 18px;}            div{margin: 0px auto;}        </style>    </head></html>                ]]></content>
      
      
      
